---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Read the Aetas Global Innovation terms of service.">
  <section class="py-24 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
      <p>Last updated: July 11, 2026</p>
      <p>By accessing the Aetas Global Innovation marketing site at Aetas.ai, you agree to comply with our Terms of Service.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">1. Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p>You agree not to probe, scan, or test the vulnerability of our website, or attempt to bypass any security gates or login blocks.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">2. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All trademarks, logos, designs, and content displayed on Aetas.ai are the property of Aetas Global Innovation or their respective owners. Unauthorized use is prohibited.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">3. Disclaimers</h2>
      <p>AI workflow automation services depend on client systems, approved data sources, implementation scope, and human validation controls. We do not guarantee specific automation outcomes, model behavior, or performance metrics unless agreed in a signed service scope.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
